# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — Research Methodology

3-layer architecture for research-backed decisions. Each layer addresses a different epistemic concern; none replaces another. Long-form reference: `{{REPO_PATH}}/docs/reference/research-synthesis-protocols.md`.
